c: 12
v: 18
t: Aur woh Yusuf ke kamees (shirt) par jhoot moot ka khoon laga kar lay aaye thay. Yeh sunkar unke baap ne kaha “balke tumhare nafs ne tumhare liye ek baday kaam ko aasaan bana diya. Accha sabr karunga aur bakhubi karunga. Jo baat tum bana rahey ho uspar Allah hi se madad maangi jaa sakti hai.”